        },
        "subject": "LU-5851 scripts: build osd-related mount dso in DKMS",
        "message": "LU-5851 scripts: build osd-related mount dso in DKMS\n\nSince LU-4606 changes, an osd-specific dso for mount command is\nshipped as part of lustre-osd RPMs. This breaks Lustre Server\nDKMS packaging which builds osd module but not this library.\n\nThis patch allows this library to be also built and installed by\nLustre Server DKMS RPM.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I479e89cef2d6b4387ee11b9119189b0141864d95\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
